    She felt that Nancy’s luv was the only thing that could save Edward. With this in mind, she resolved to divorce Edward (or obtain a dispensation from <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    She felt that Nancy’s luv was the only thing that could save Edward. With this in mind, she resolved to divorce Edward (or obtain a dispensation from Rome), thereby permitting Edward and Nancy to marry. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
